title: RIP#4 - New Reserve Bonds
body:
To increase diversification of the treasury, we need to list new bonds and increase backing.

This proposal is an open proposal to see the sentiment of what assets are most favoured to be added to the Treasury.

The reserve that receives the most votes, will have a bond depository deployed within 48 hours of proposal commencing.

You can weight your votes over multiple choices...
